&lt;li&gt;Design scalable, collaborative, and social online learning experiences used by Fortune 500 companies, universities, and training organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own 1-2 major projects at any time, serving as the design lead who shapes solutions from initial problem exploration through final implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the product management team to frame problems, define project scope, explore multiple design approaches, and make well-reasoned recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide production-ready mocks and assets, and work closely with engineers to balance quality and feasibility&lt;/li&gt;
